sentences.english: I always stick to be virginity to present the man who I will live together throughout my life.
sentences.chinese: 总是守着着份贞操留给和自己一辈子的男人。

sentences.english: A wartermelon is cut into four equal pieces.
sentences.chinese: 一个西瓜被切成四等份。

sentences.english: We made good proposals to Taye but he refused.

sentences.english: With flame retardant more than 5 parts added, the flammability of the board is reduced.

sentences.english: What are your thoughts about a company designating a portion of its annual profits for philanthropy?
sentences.chinese: 对于公司每年提拨一部份利润作慈善，你有何看法？

sentences.english: We have to retain our best customer. We have to be there.
sentences.chinese: 我们必须获得那份销售合同，留住最好的客户。

sentences.english: I'm happy to be a part of a team that's a contender and looking forward to playoffs.
sentences.chinese: 我是快乐是一个竞争者的队一部份而且期望延长加赛。
